{
  "stem": "21308.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Now I reckon this would be between 1:00 and 2:00.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "It might have been a little before 1:00.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And as I went in through the gates, I realized that, just merely looking at the place, that this had been at one time a military establishment.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Just what sort of, I didn't know then.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And these people had gone-- be pushed into there for convenience sake.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Somebody had to put them somewhere and didn't know where else to put them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And I noticed, as soon as I got inside this barracks, or as the Germans call it, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I realized there was a football field there, and this camp was built round this football field.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Not an unusual thing to do, really.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And there were people everywhere in concentration camp kit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Old clothes which they had picked up from somewhere.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "All ages, old woman, old man, babies.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Terrible mess it was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Terrible mess.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was told that the armored car regiment was in there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only-- the only bit of the British army which I saw was one officer who was a-- I think he was a captain, and his armored car.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said to him, I'd come in to take over this lot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What can you tell me about it?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, not very much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, I know a meal is on its way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We've got some cooks cooking a meal.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But I don't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, I just don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said, I tried to put them in that nationalities, and they won't go into nationalities.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They prefer to be in their camps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's why I knew that there was more than one camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so he said, well, I can't tell you anything else.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know anything else.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
